      {
        "id": "comment_intro",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 📄 Meeting Transcript Summarizer\n\nTurn a meeting into clean notes and a to-do list — from either a recording or an already-typed transcript.\n\n**Pipeline:** Recording OR Transcript → (transcribe if needed) → merge → Summarize + Extract action items\n\nOnly one of the two inputs is required. If you paste a transcript, Whisper is skipped entirely — that's why this replaces the old 'Summarize Audio' template rather than sitting next to it.\n\n**Try this:** paste minutes from a call instead of uploading audio, or ask for action items grouped by owner."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 30,
            "y": -260
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 520,
          "height": 210,
          "selectable": true
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
